, holo-, P): 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[890,903,1568,1586]" pageId="8" pageNumber="23">A</emphasis>
, aspect général; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1049,1062,1568,1586]" pageId="8" pageNumber="23">B</emphasis>
